<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="02 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话说，上次我回老家的时候，<delay20 />
翻出了好多<delay8 />小时候画的画。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />学校上课时画了妈妈的画像<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为当时刚和妈妈吵了一架，<delay20 />
所以画的是她生气的脸。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，后来觉得这样不好，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在和妈妈和好以后，<delay8 />
我就用蜡笔强行改成了笑脸。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后，<delay8 />就成了这样<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还挺……<delay frames="40" />
前卫的<delay8 />作品了呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有我爸爸做的料理的画！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次他做了好吃的料理，<delay20 />
我就会画一张画<delay8 />作为谢礼。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过<delay8 />饭菜吃完了，<delay8 />
就不能照着实物画了。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以，<delay20 />
大多数画<delay8 />都很难分辨
到底画的是什么<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那样又旧又难看的画，<delay8 />
明明早就该扔掉了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但父母还是要留着。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我之前总觉得<delay8 />父母特别唠叨。<delay20 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但他们做的事，<delay8 />
让我很感动呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="010_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道<delay8 />亲戚家的孩子们
最近好吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然难得才能见一次，<delay20 />
不过每次见面，<delay8 />他们都会叫着姐姐、姐姐，
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对我撒娇，<delay8 />超级可爱！<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了！<delay frames="40" />这些<delay8 /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" />的<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />，
下次有机会给他们带过去吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像，<delay20 />最近挺受欢迎的一个搞笑艺人<delay8 />
是我的远房亲戚呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没想到，<delay8 />我还有当艺人的亲戚啊！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然我们有血缘关系，<delay8 />
是不是我身上也有搞笑才能呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />不过我好像从没有觉得<delay20 />
那个艺人抖的包袱好笑呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有个亲戚<delay8 />是学校的老师呢！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那人严肃得<delay20 />让我怀疑，<delay8 />
是真的和我有血缘关系吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次遇到那个人，<delay20 />
就让我想起，<delay8 />在我叛逆的学生时代，<delay8 />
认真用心教导我的班主任老师。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我亲戚的学生里也有像当年的我一样的，<delay20 />
一定每天都很辛苦吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="020_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我每次看到<delay20 />射击游戏的摊位，<delay8 />
总忍不住要去挑战一下。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说来，<delay20 />我之前还跟一个
和<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" />长得一模一样的家伙<delay8 />
比赛过射击游戏呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你问比赛结果如何？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那当然是<delay8 />我完胜了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />小的时候，<delay20 />每次去逛庙会，<delay8 />
我都会缠着父母买面具呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当然了，他们不会每次都给我买。<delay20 />
所以每次买到面具，我都会高兴得<delay8 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />回到家了<delay8 />都不肯摘。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />你这是<delay8 />什么眼神？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也是有过
可爱的时候的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我从小就特别喜欢<delay20 />
小摊上卖的迷你蜂蜜蛋糕。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在逛庙会的时候，<delay8 />
边走边吃着刚出炉的蜂蜜蛋糕，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比任何高级的蛋糕<delay8 />都要好吃呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="030_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有过<delay8 />打工的经历吗？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我第一次打工，<delay20 />
被父母反对说<delay8 />年纪还太小。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但因为我有无论如何都想买的东西，<delay20 />
只好反复求他们<delay8 />允许我去打工。<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那份工作<delay8 />我干了挺长时间的呢。<delay20 />
家里人都很意外，没想到我能坚持那么久！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他们都太小看我的毅力了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很多年前，<delay20 />
我在游艺中心当过店员。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一天<delay8 />我看到一个人在玩我当时很喜欢的
一个节奏游戏，<delay20 />打出了让人难以置信的高分！<delay20 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看完<delay8 />我就忍不住了！<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我向那家伙发起了挑战，<delay8 />一直比到店关门呢。<delay frames="30" />
哎呀～<delay8 />当时战况可激烈了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过那天<delay8 />没能拿到工资。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在这座<tag a="110" b="32" />上做DIY的时候，<delay20 />
总会想起之前<delay8 />
在老家的<delay8 />家居中心打工的日子。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那里有卖花苗，<delay8 />还有卖一些不知道
有什么用的工具，<delay20 />品种超多，可有意思了～<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了对了！<delay20 />我还记得有一个<delay8 />
喜欢做DIY的，手很巧的常客！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是那人来这里<delay8 />肯定就成英雄了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="040" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="040_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以前我还在老家生活的时候，<delay20 />
经常和父母发生冲突。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在离开老家才觉得，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />父母是因为关心我<delay20 />
才会来<delay20 />管教我的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然想到了，<delay20 />
偶尔也给老家寄张心意卡吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="040_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像这样一起聊聊天，<delay20 />
互相寄寄心意卡<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样的行为对于我们来说是理所当然的事，<delay20 />
但能拥有这样的朋友<delay8 />
绝对不是理所当然的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然事到如今再说这样的话很难为情，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我还是要说，一直以来真的很谢谢你！<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="3" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="040_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我以前啊<tag a="110" b="0" />很叛逆的，<delay20 />
不会坦率地说出<delay8 />“谢谢你”这句话。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在我向那时候的朋友<delay8 />表达了我的心意，<delay20 />
他们都可高兴了！<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉我们之间的关系<delay8 />也更亲密了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也应该对父母<delay8 />好好表达我的心意呢～<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay20 />要是我说出那么肉麻的话，<delay20 />
他们可能会吓得腿软吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="050" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="050_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前段时间，<delay8 />我在老家找到了很久以前的照片，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是我的祖母的祖母，<delay20 />
年轻时候的照片。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也不清楚她是个什么样性格的人，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但一想到，<delay8 />因为有她的存在才有现在的我，<delay20 />
就感觉心口热热的呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="050_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到自己小时候的照片，<delay20 />
总感觉很不好意思，不敢直视呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还穿着肥大的<delay8 />土里土气的运动服。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看着相册，
能回想起许多以前的事情，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就这一点来说<delay8 />还是很棒的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="050_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />打扫房间的时候，<delay8 />我翻到了以前的照片，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />照片上是小时候的我，<delay8 />
和我当时的玩伴。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />已经很多年没见过了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要不要试着<delay8 />打个电话呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对方一定会被吓到吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="060" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="060_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以前我和<delay20 />附近的孩子王打架，
怎么都打不过，那真叫一个气……<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但又不想认输，硬是憋着不哭出来。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后我妈妈就这么对我说：<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“大胆哭吧，<delay20 />哭证明你心中有热血。”<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听到这句话我才终于痛哭了一场。
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后呢，<delay20 />第二天<delay20 />我算是彻底放下了包袱，
很轻松地就把那孩子王打倒了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当时我心里真的，<delay20 />不知道多感谢我妈妈！</message>
	<message label="060_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我以前<delay20 />脾气可是非常暴躁的。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />妈妈总是让我<anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再稳重一些，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为这件事也没少挨她骂。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过有一天，<delay20 />我死党被人欺负的时候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Fuming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我冲上去就喊，<delay frames="40" />“你们干什么！”<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然后把那帮小坏蛋都赶跑了。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />死党对我说谢谢的时候啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是打心底里觉得，<delay8 />虽然这样对不起妈妈，
但要少了这暴脾气，<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就不是我了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="060_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那是我刚离开家里出来住的时候吧，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />附近的超市里围绕特价蔬菜爆发了一场大战，<delay8 />
现在回想起来也真是壮烈啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我算是不自量力地加入到
那些强者们的战斗中，<delay20 /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />跟你说啊，
当时要是不用出十二分本事，<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />早就被打趴了。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果我也算买到了想要的菜，<delay8 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是包装在大战中受损，菜叶也软趴趴了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是换我妈妈来，应该轻松就能拿下吧。</message>
	<message label="070" attrib="47 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />朋友的孩子之前问我，<delay20 />
想给妈妈准备礼物，<delay8 />应该送什么好。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实，<delay8 />我也想不出啥特别的建议……</message>
	<message label="071" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="071_01" attrib="48 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就向那孩子推荐<delay20 />送一束花。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />平时也没什么机会收到花，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />应该会感觉挺特别的吧？</message>
	<message label="071_02" attrib="48 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就向那孩子推荐送“捶背券”。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自己的孩子给自己按摩，<delay8 />想想都很棒！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />疲劳什么的<delay8 />肯定能一扫而空！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="071_03" attrib="48 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想着，<delay8 />不管在什么年龄收到都会很开心的，<delay20 />
应该就是信件了吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />收到孩子亲手写的信件，<delay20 />肯定会看哭吧！</message>
	<message label="071_04" attrib="48 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想，能收到亲手做的料理应该会很高兴吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />那么小的孩子要一个人做料理还太早，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且也太危险了，<delay8 />所以我打算去帮个忙。</message>
	<message label="072" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话说，<delay20 />这么小就能想着母亲，<delay8 />
想让她高兴，<delay20 />真的很了不起呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也要<delay8 />向那孩子学习～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>